[Nouns] contraposition, opposition; polarity; inversion [more]; opposite side; reverse, inverse; counterpart; antipodes; opposite poles, North and South.
antonym, opposite (contrariety) [more].
[Verbs] be opposite; subtend.
[Adjectives] opposite; reverse, inverse; converse, antipodal, subcontrary; fronting, facing, diametrically opposite, diametrically opposed.
Northern, septentrional, Boreal, arctic; Southern, Austral, Antarctic.
[Adverbs] over, over the way, over against; against; face to face, vis-a-vis; as poles asunder.
